statements: SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC;
SELECT training_id, log_message FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE training_id = 100;
SELECT log_id, log_timestamp FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE log_timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs ORDER BY log_id ASC;
SELECT training_id, log_message FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE log_message LIKE '%error%';
SELECT log_id, training_id, log_timestamp, log_message FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs;
SELECT log_message, log_timestamp, training_id, log_id FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE training_id = 10 ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC;
SELECT log_id, log_message FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE training_id IN (1, 2, 3) AND log_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs WHERE training_id = 5 ORDER BY log_timestamp ASC, log_id DESC;
SELECT training_id, COUNT(*) AS total_logs FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingLogs GROUP BY training_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 100;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_logs WHERE training_loss > 0.5;
SELECT log_id, training_accuracy FROM neural_network_logs WHERE training_accuracy BETWEEN 0.7 AND 0.9;
SELECT training_loss, training_accuracy FROM neural_network_logs ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT log_id, optimization_accuracy FROM optimization_logs WHERE optimization_loss < 0.3;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_logs WHERE training_accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY log_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_logs WHERE training_accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT log_id, training_loss FROM neural_network_logs WHERE training_loss < 0.5 ORDER BY log_id ASC
SELECT AVG(training_accuracy) AS average_accuracy, MAX(training_loss) AS highest_loss FROM neural_network_logs
SELECT * FROM optimization_logs WHERE optimization_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND optimization_accuracy BETWEEN 0.7 AND 0.9 ORDER BY optimization_timestamp DESC
SELECT MIN(training_loss) AS lowest_training_loss, COUNT(log_id) AS num_logs FROM neural_network_logs
SELECT * FROM neural_network_logs;
SELECT message, timestamp FROM neural_network_logs WHERE log_id = 1;
SELECT model_name, epoch, loss, accuracy FROM training_progress WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM training_progress ORDER BY epoch DESC;
SELECT optimizer_name, learning_rate FROM optimizer_logs WHERE momentum < 0.5;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT log_id, timestamp, message FROM neural_network_logs WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-06-30';
SELECT progress_id, model_name, epoch, loss, accuracy FROM training_progress WHERE accuracy >= 0.9 ORDER BY epoch DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM optimizer_logs WHERE learning_rate > 0.001 AND momentum < 0.9 ORDER BY optimizer_id ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT optimizer_name, COUNT(optimizer_id) AS total_logs FROM optimizer_logs GROUP BY optimizer_name HAVING total_logs > 5 ORDER BY total_logs DESC;
SELECT * FROM neural_networks;
SELECT network_name, training_status FROM neural_networks;
SELECT training_start_time, training_end_time FROM neural_networks;
SELECT * FROM loss_logs ORDER BY epoch_number DESC;
SELECT network_id, loss_value, validation_loss FROM loss_logs WHERE network_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM neural_networks;
SELECT network_name, training_start_time, training_status FROM neural_networks WHERE training_status='completed';
SELECT network_name, training_start_time, training_end_time FROM neural_networks WHERE training_status='in_progress' ORDER BY training_start_time DESC;
SELECT network_name, training_status, training_end_time FROM neural_networks WHERE training_end_time IS NOT NULL AND training_status='completed';

SELECT nn.network_name, ll.epoch_number, ll.loss_value, ll.validation_loss FROM neural_networks nn JOIN loss_logs ll ON nn.id = ll.network_id WHERE loss_value < 0.1 ORDER BY validation_loss ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkModel;
SELECT model_name, loss FROM NeuralNetworkModel WHERE model_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM TrainingLog ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT model_name, batch_size FROM Hyperparameters JOIN NeuralNetworkModel ON Hyperparameters.model_id = NeuralNetworkModel.model_id;
SELECT log_message, error_message FROM TrainingLog JOIN ErrorLog ON TrainingLog.log_id = ErrorLog.log_id;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkModel ORDER BY model_id DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT model_name, loss FROM NeuralNetworkModel WHERE loss > 0.5 AND model_name LIKE '%Neural%' ORDER BY model_id ASC;
SELECT model_name, training_start_date, training_end_date FROM NeuralNetworkModel WHERE training_start_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY training_start_date ASC LIMIT 2;

SELECT model_id, training_start_date, training_end_date, loss FROM NeuralNetworkModel JOIN Hyperparameters ON NeuralNetworkModel.model_id = Hyperparameters.model_id WHERE learning_rate < 0.01 AND batch_size = 64 ORDER BY model_id ASC;

SELECT model_name, log_timestamp, log_message FROM NeuralNetworkModel INNER JOIN TrainingLog ON NeuralNetworkModel.model_id = TrainingLog.model_id WHERE log_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
